::Hot Rod::

He saw her blush. He sipped some more energin.
"The pleasure is all mine."

::DrillBit::

He stayed next to KitKat, doing what ever he could, to keep her alive.
"Dont leave me, not now. I'll wait here for your answer"
He turned away and prayed.
"Please dont her from me, Vector Sigma. Dont take her to the Matrix,
yet." He went back to working on her.
